### Full API docs here: https://assess-risks-and-needs-dev.hmpps.service.justice.gov.uk/swagger-ui/index.html

### Get current risk scores (old)
GET {{arnsHost}}/risks/crn/{{crn}}/predictors/all
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("token")}}

### Get current risk scores (V2)
GET {{arnsHost}}/risks/predictors/all/crn/{{crn}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("token")}}

### Get risk summary
GET {{arnsHost}}/risks/crn/{{crn}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("token")}}
